The invention discloses a rotating and slide die set of a portable terminal and a portable terminal adopted the die set, wherein the rotating and slide die set comprises a first slide board, a second slide board which is slidably connected with the first slide board, the die set further comprises a base plate and a rotating shaft, wherein the base plate is provided with a pivoting hole for the rotating shaft to thread and pivot, and the rotating shaft is fixed on the surface of the second slide adjacent to the side after threading the pivoting hole. The portable terminal further comprises a cover and a main body which is fixed with the base plate, and the cover is fixed with the first slide board. The cover of the invention is also basically symmetrical relative to the main body after rotating, simultaneously enlarges the opening area of the main body after rotating to open, meets the requirement of key-press arrangement, and the rotating and slide die set of the invention has thin thickness, which reduces the thickness of the portable terminal, and meets the portable and light requirements of users.

